NAME

warnings::method - Produces warnings if methods are called as functions

SYNOPSIS

	use warnings::method;  # installs the check routine as 'syntax'
	use warnings 'syntax'; # enables  the check routine

	Or, try "perl -Mblib example/synopsis.pl" after "make test".

INSTALLATION

	To install this module, run the following commands:

		perl Makefile.PL
		make
		make test
		make install

DEPENDENCIES

	Perl 5.8.1 or later, and a C compiler.

